<font color="#FF0000">WHAT A MAN, WHAT AN EXPERIENCE</font><br>
<tt>Wed Jul 23 18:54:50 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Some time ago I was in the presence of a very well-known Native American actor -- a person to whom I regarded with respect and honor. I was astounded at his reaction when he came across an old buddy from his tour of duty. Tears, hugs, a real friendship and bond formulated out of an experience that I will never fully understand. To this day I will never forget how this man whom I revered and put on a pededstal became an even greater human being in my eyes.<br>
Thank you.
